Find out more about the movies you want to see, buy tickets, access your AMC Stubs account and pre-order food and drinks!

•	See a Movie: Swipe to see what’s playing now, or coming soon to a theatre near you. Buy tickets for a showtime today, or get tickets to an upcoming movie showing to make sure you won’t miss it.

•	Our Theatres: Type in the name of your favorite theatre, or find the theatre closest to you. Find out which theatres feature premium formats like Dolby Cinema at AMC, IMAX and AMC, or RealD 3D.

•	All About Movies: Discover AMC exclusives, official trailers, movie synopses, cast info, and film ratings from experts like IMDb and Rotten Tomatoes.

•	AMC Stubs: Log into your AMC Stubs Insider or Premiere account to access your virtual card and add it to your mobile wallet. Use your virtual card to get rewards like a free large popcorn refill, or free popcorn and fountain drink size upgrades for Premiere members. Plus, you can track your points and activate or view your rewards while on the go.

•	My AMC: Find your purchased tickets, upcoming movies and important special offers. Set reminders for movies you want to see, and we’ll tell you as soon as tickets go on sale.

•	Food and Drinks Online Ordering: Skip the line by ordering concessions before you get to the theatre. Available at select locations with either express pick-up at the concession stand, or delivery to your seat.